      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like there's no path back from this. i was someone. people respected me. now, i'm just a cautionary tale for people to point at. even the idea of \"starting over\" feels like a joke. how do you rebuild when the foundation itself is rotten? it's just... so much work for nothing.",
